  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This adversary posseses the Ketsuryūgan, granting them the following benefits when active; </p><ul><li><p>60 feet of chakra sight. </p></li><li><p>Resistance to Necrotic damage and immunity to bleeding. </p></li><li><p>When you deal cold damage, you can change the damage type to necrotic and add your Wisdom modifier to the damage dealt, or increase the Save DC by +1. </p></li><li><p>When a hostile creature in combat takes damage from the <em><strong>bleeding</strong></em> condition, increase the damage dealt by 1 step.</p></li></ul>",
